@startuml
title Study App - Development Process with Quality Helpers

start
:1) Implement change\n(code + docs);

#E8F5E9:2) Helper command\n`make docs-fix`\n(regenerates docs artifacts);

:3) Local quality gate\n`make verify` + `make docs-check`;

if (Local checks green?) then (yes)
else (no)
  :Fix locally and rerun\n`make verify` + `make docs-check`;
  -up-> :3) Local quality gate\n`make verify` + `make docs-check`;
endif

:4) Open/Update PR;
#E8F5E9:Helper in CI\n`.github/workflows/pr-template-check.yml`;

:5) CI quality gate\n(full pipeline checks);

if (CI green?) then (yes)
  :6) Review and merge;
else (no)
  :Fix in branch;\nRun `make verify` + `make docs-check`;\nPush updates;
  -up-> :5) CI quality gate\n(full pipeline checks);
endif

stop

@enduml
